## 📋 Recipe 3: AI-Powered App
**Stack**: Next.js → Supabase → OpenAI or Anthropic → Stripe → Netlify

### Build Sequence
```
Phase 1:
Build an AI [type] app with Next.js. Pages: /chat (main interface),
/history (saved conversations), /settings, /pricing.
Clean chat UI with message bubbles, input field, and send button.

Phase 2:
Connect Supabase. Tables:
- conversations: id, user_id, title (text), created_at
- messages: id, conversation_id, role (text: 'user' | 'assistant'),
  content (text), created_at
RLS: users access only their own conversations and messages.

Phase 3:
Connect [OpenAI/Anthropic]. Add streaming chat responses.
System prompt: "You are a [role]. [Constraints and purpose]."
On each user message: save to messages table, call AI API,
stream response to UI, save assistant response to messages table.

Phase 4:
Add rate limiting: free users get [X] messages/day, pro users unlimited.
Track usage in Supabase. Show usage meter in the UI.
Connect Stripe to gate pro features.
```

