## 📋 Recipe 4: Content Site / Blog
**Stack**: Next.js → Strapi or Directus → Netlify → Google Analytics

### Build Sequence
```
Phase 1:
Build a blog with Next.js. Pages: / (home with latest posts),
/blog (all posts with categories), /blog/[slug] (post detail),
/about, /contact.
Clean reading-focused design with good typography.

Phase 2:
Connect [Strapi/Directus] as headless CMS.
Content types: articles (title, slug, body, excerpt, cover_image,
author, category, published_at), categories (name, slug).
Fetch articles via the CMS REST API on page load.

Phase 3:
Add SEO: dynamic meta tags and Open Graph tags on each article page
using the article title, excerpt, and cover image.
Add an RSS feed at /rss.xml.
```

