## When to Use Which Recipe

| User wants to build | Send them |
|---|---|
| Subscription product with users | Recipe 1: SaaS |
| Online store selling products | Recipe 2: E-Commerce |
| App using AI/ChatGPT | Recipe 3: AI App |
| Blog or content website | Recipe 4: Content Site |
| Appointment or service booking | Recipe 5: Booking App |
| Collect leads and email them | Recipe 6: Lead Gen |

