## Recipes Troubleshooting

### SaaS: Stripe subscription not reflected in app after payment
- Webhook not reaching the app — add webhook endpoint to Stripe Dashboard
- Raw body not parsed before signature verification
- Fix: see rocket-troubleshooting.mdc → Stripe section

### SaaS: New users see blank dashboard (no data)
- Supabase profile trigger not created — run the trigger prompt from Phase 2
- RLS too restrictive — check policies allow users to read their own rows

### E-Commerce: Inventory not updating after purchase
- Webhook handler not decrementing inventory
- Fix: add inventory decrement logic in the `checkout.session.completed` handler

### AI App: Messages not persisting across sessions
- Conversation ID not stored in localStorage or URL
- Fix: save `conversation_id` to URL params or Supabase on first message

### All Recipes: Production deploy issues
- See the ⚠️ Go-Live Checklist in Recipe 1 — applies to all recipes
- Most common: Stripe webhook secret mismatch and missing Supabase redirect URLs

